The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

awaaz Teri soniye surili noori vargi jaddo lakh Hilda odo ta nora lagdi

hune  mei banada menu das da sahi Jaan mangla mei tereto Jaan varda appe niklugi tu hass ta sahi tere vich Nasha pehle todh da kude

snippet.title: Bajaj Freedom CNG Bike - Kya Sahi, Kya Nahi | First Look
snippet.description: Bajaj CNG motorcycle - Freedom 125 - has finally gone on sale in India at a starting price of Rs 95,000 whereas the top-end Disc brake + LED light version costs Rs 1.10 lacs (ex-showroom). What makes it unique is the fact that it gets a 2KG CNG tank beneath the seat and a 2-litre petrol fuel tank. cumulatively, both offer a range of 330Km (realistic range). On CNG alone, it offers over 108kmpl thus making it the most fuel efficient motorcycle on sale in India right now. Hope you enjoy this video.

This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainmentâ€™s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death.
